code: @Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeString(processorTag).     if (ingestDocument == null) {         out.writeBoolean(false).     } else {         out.writeBoolean(true).         ingestDocument.writeTo(out).     }     out.writeException(failure). }

ElasticsearchException.generateFailureXContent(builder, params, failure, true).         builder.endObject().     } else if (failure != null) {         ElasticsearchException.generateFailureXContent(builder, params, failure, true).     }     if (ingestDocument != null) {         ingestDocument.toXContent(builder, params).     }     builder.endObject().     return builder. }
